Ukraine: Families are desperate, cold, afraid &amp; hungry. 

@WFP is setting up emergency operations to provide food assistance to people affected by the conflict, including families fleeing to neighboring countries.

https://t.co/QwSmU8jd3D

The military operations in Ukraine have caused families to flee their homes for neighbouring countries.

@Refugees remains firmly committed to supporting all those affected.

Learn how you can help: https://t.co/kIK3kiSG8u https://t.co/wEL4g2aLRW

Ukraine: Intensifying hostilities are threatening the safety of tens of thousands of families,

@UNOCHA &amp; partners are committed to staying &amp; delivering assistance, but immediate support is needed.
https://t.co/fd4PWlRawk

“There are no winners in war, but countless lives will be torn apart.” 

@Refugees chief @FilippoGrandi and other UN officials warn of the devastating consequences of military action in Ukraine.
https://t.co/rlF7AhDZpi
